fields.physical_description:
1. instructions booklet printed to show the title and maker's details together with text and identification of parts. The shaped blocks and slabs are made of oak with the blocks fastened together with oak pins and the slabs with tongues. This method is reflected in the name Pin-Tung. 
2,3. blocks; each with 8 holes drilled into each surface and one at each end with grooves also cut into the long surfaces. 6in x 3/4insq 
4,5. blocks; as 2 and 3 but with 5 holes. 3 3/4in x 3/4in square 
6-11. blocks; as 2 and 3 but with 4 holes. 3in x 3/4in sq. 
12,13. blocks; as 2 and 3 but with 3 holes. 2¼in x 3/4in sq. 
14-17. blocks; as 2 and 3 but with 2 holes. 1½in x 3/4insq. 
18,19. blocks; as 2 and 3 but with 1 hole. 3/4in cube 
20-22. slabs; with a groove cut into each side. 3 x 1 x ¼in 
23-27. slabs; as (20). 3in x 3/4in x ¼in 
28-30. slabs; as (20) with a hole drilled through one end. 3in x 3/4in x ¼in 
31-33. slabs; as (20). 2¼in x 3/4in x ¼in 
34,35. arch; with 4 holes drilled through. 3in x 1½in x 3/4in 
36. round block; with large hole drilled through centre. 2in x diam 1¼in 37. rod. L. 7in 
38. thin rod. L. 3 3/4in 
39. semicircle; 1½in x 5/8in x 1/8in 
40. 'r' shape. Ht. 1½in x gt. w. 7/8in x 1/8in 
41. washer with hole drilled through. diam ½in 
42. pulley wheel with hole and groove. diam ½in 
43. pulley wheel with hole; side and top grooves. diam ½in 
44. box; covered with buff coloured paper; stamped PINS PIN-TUNG containing wooden pins of various sizes 
45. box; covered with buff coloured paper; stamped TONGUES PIN-TUNG containing wooden tongues of various sizes 
46. box lid; sliding; with paper label printed in a few colours to show the title and maker's details; a photograph of a boy playing with the pieces and another showing models which could be made from the set 
47. box base; with label printed in green to read PINTUNG MECHANICAL BUILDING BLOCKS No 1.; and a price label A W GAMAGES Ltd 2/6 LONDON EC
fields.title: Pin-Tung Mechanical Building Blocks
fields.marks: shield shape with crossed arrows and the name TESSTED TOYS THAT TEACH
